    "<div style=\"background:#101210;border:1px solid #2b2e26;border-left:3px solid #5FD87A;padding:16px 20px;margin:0 0 16px 0;border-radius:0;\"><div style=\"font-family:'Courier New',ui-monospace,monospace;padding:10px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #2b2e26;\"><span style=\"font-family:'Courier New',ui-monospace,monospace;font-size:11px;letter-spacing:1px;text-transform:uppercase;color:#5FD87A;border:1px solid #5FD87A;padding:2px 6px;border-radius:0;\">FACILITATES</span> &nbsp; <span style=\"color:#E7E9E2;font-size:12px;\">Ghaf \u2192 Al Arta</span><div style=\"color:#83897C;font-size:12px;margin-top:4px;\">Nitrogen-fixing root nodules improve adjacent soil fertility.</div></div><div style=\"font-family:'Courier New',ui-monospace,monospace;padding:10px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #2b2e26;\"><span style=\"font-family:'Courier New',ui-monospace,monospace;font-size:11px;letter-spacing:1px;text-transform:uppercase;color:#5FD87A;border:1px solid #5FD87A;padding:2px 6px;border-radius:0;\">FACILITATES</span> &nbsp; <span style=\"color:#E7E9E2;font-size:12px;\">Sidr \u2192 Saltbush</span><div style=\"color:#83897C;font-size:12px;margin-top:4px;\">Canopy shade reduces understorey evapotranspiration stress.</div></div><div style=\"font-family:'Courier New',ui-monospace,monospace;padding:10px 0;\"><span style=\"font-family:'Courier New',ui-monospace,monospace;font-size:11px;letter-spacing:1px;text-transform:uppercase;color:#F0C338;border:1px solid #F0C338;padding:2px 6px;border-radius:0;\">WATCH</span> &nbsp; <span style=\"color:#E7E9E2;font-size:12px;\">Ghaf \u2194 Arabian Acacia</span><div style=\"color:#83897C;font-size:12px;margin-top:4px;\">Root competition at &lt;4m spacing \u2014 stagger planting distance.</div></div></div>"
